HEADWORD: Alluminor
<hw>Al*lu"mi*nor</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF.
<ets>alumineor</ets>, fr. L. <ets>ad</ets> + <ets>liminare</ets>. See
<er>Luminate</er>.]</ety> <def>An illuminator of manuscripts and books;
a limner.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Cowell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

